<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1554724-are-the-scenes-of-sexual-abuse-graphic-in">Are the scenes of sexual abuse graphic in nature, or is it just mentioned, as in that these acts were occurring but not much detail is given?</a>
</div>
