<span id="freeTextContainer14321883962695458034">The Nickel academy is one fucking scary reform school in 1960’s Florida, where blacks were very much discriminated against. <br/>Rather than going to Juvie, troubled boys were sent here. Corporal punishments being handed out more than a washroom pass.<br/><br/>Elwood, a young boy of 16 hoping to go to college with his big dreams and Martin Luther king playing in his head, hitches a ride unknowingly in a stolen car. And his sentence to the Nickel academy begins. where one rare friendship is made.<br/>Here kids are b</span>
  <span id="freeText14321883962695458034" style="display:none">The Nickel academy is one fucking scary reform school in 1960’s Florida, where blacks were very much discriminated against. <br />Rather than going to Juvie, troubled boys were sent here. Corporal punishments being handed out more than a washroom pass.<br /><br />Elwood, a young boy of 16 hoping to go to college with his big dreams and Martin Luther king playing in his head, hitches a ride unknowingly in a stolen car. And his sentence to the Nickel academy begins. where one rare friendship is made.<br />Here kids are broken and left with scars daily -physically and spiritually. <br />Brutality in its rawest forms. <br />This is one powerful and tragic story.<br />5⭐️</span>
